The purpose of creating a group allows other users to join them, typically to assimilate an audience such as a fanbase or [[Special:MyLanguage/Community:Culture|culture]], and optionally, to host and participate in [[Special:MyLanguage/Calendar|events]] within group [[Special:MyLanguage/Instances|instances]]. Members of a group may choose to represent it, showcasing the group's banner on their nameplate and profile. The Groups feature was officially released on [https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/vrchat-groups November 30th, 2022].